    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for everything from grocery runs to weekend road trips. It drives like a dream and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. If you're looking for a great, well-loved car that\u2019s ready to go, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera offers a visceral, analog driving experience powered by a 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine. The M96 powerplant, paired with a 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle, utilizes Variocam Plus for a broad powerband and urgent throttle response. The chassis maintains its precision, featuring a sophisticated multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts that deliver the signature communicative steering feel Porsche is known for. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including cooling system optimization and IMS bearing verification, ensuring the mechanical integrity of the drivetrain. While the exterior shows the light patina of a well-loved driver's car, the structural rigidity and aerodynamic efficiency remain uncompromised. This is a mechanically sorted example optimized for spirited performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used sedan. Clean title. Recent service history included. Reliable engine. Minor exterior wear. Interior is clean.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
