    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-maintained, reliable machine that has been cared for with a focus on longevity. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor surface-level imperfections and small stone chips consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and remains smoke-free; the leather seating is supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the premium infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound and drives beautifully. It features a complete service log, with a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection performed just last month. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car offers a smooth, quiet ride and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 31500.0,
