    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking and driving great. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for your next adventure, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32000.0,
